                            <head>266. Editorial Note</head>
                            <p>A memorandum of a conversation regarding Cyprus, March 20, held at
                                the Mid-Ocean Club among President <persName corresp="#p_EDD1">Eisenhower</persName>, Secretary <persName corresp="#p_DJF1">Dulles</persName>, Prime Minister <persName corresp="#p_MH1">Macmillan</persName>, and Foreign Secretary <persName corresp="#p_LSJSB1">Lloyd</persName>, is quoted in an editorial
                                note in volume XXIV, page 464.</p>
                        </div>
